title: Fall Indoor Volleyball Leagues
text: Games at 8:00 PM / 9:00 PM Wednesday Nights at Dive Volleyball (Denver) Coed 4's Intermediate/Advanced Division Coed 6's Recreational and Intermediate Divisions Games at 6:00 PM / 7:00 PM / 8:00 PM / 9:00 PM Thursday Nights at Front Range Community College (Westminster) Coed 6's Recreational/Intermediate Skill Level Games at 6:30 / 7:20 / 8:10 / 9:00 Thursday Night Indoor Sand Volleyball at Aces Volleyball Facility (Monument) Coed 4's Recreational ("Beer League") Intermediate Men's 4's Intermediate Games at 7:00 / 8:00 / 9:00 PM! All leagues are 7 match seasons (3 games to 25 rally scoring) and include a big end of season tournament for all Coed 4's indoor teams and Coed 6's indoor teams. 4's - self-officiated 6's - paid official included $49 per player for 6's $69 per player for 4's $280 per team for 4's $300 per team for 6's Please note that RSVP'ing for this meetup does not guarantee you a spot in our leagues, you need to submit a TEAM or INDIVIDUAL registration form and e-mail it to WePlay@MileHighSSC.com Dive Volleyball, 2335 Delgany St, Denver Front Range Community College, 645 West 112th Avenue, Westminster Aces Volleyball Facility, 16815 Mitchell Road, Monument Location
